# Custom domain — placeholder
#
# When you own a domain (e.g. notchy.dev / notchy.app / notchy.otaru.tech),
# rename this file to `CNAME` (no extension) and put a single line in it
# with your domain name:
#
#     notchy.dev
#
# Then add the DNS records at your registrar:
#
#   For an apex domain (notchy.dev):
#     A   @   185.199.108.153
#     A   @   185.199.109.153
#     A   @   185.199.110.153
#     A   @   185.199.111.153
#
#   For a subdomain (www.notchy.dev or notchy.otaru.tech):
#     CNAME  www  otarutech.github.io.
#
# GitHub Pages will issue a free Let's Encrypt cert automatically once
# DNS resolves (~15 min after change). After that the site is live at
# https://notchy.dev/ with the same content currently at
# https://otarutech.github.io/notchy/.
#
# Don't forget to update:
#   - <meta property="og:url"> in docs/index.html
#   - og:image URL and twitter:image URL in docs/index.html
#   - README link
